location.fullValue: Salerno Plan, Saguaro Reserve at Dove Mountain

data.description: Welcome home to this fabulous property in gated & desirable Blue Agave at Dove Mountain. This Peralta model by Mattamy homes offers 2 BD/2BA/1,810 Sq.Ft + Den. Enter through the spacious paver courtyard to this spacious floorplan that offers a large family room, dining area off kitchen & split bedroom plan. Kitchen offers granite counters, upgraded white cabinets, stainless steel appliances, island w/sink & breakfast bar & walk-in pantry. Primary suite has dual vanities, separate walk-in shower & tub & spacious walk-in closet. Relax in the backyard under the covered patio and enjoy the east facing views & manicured landscaping. Garage has epoxy floors, utility sink & extra space for workshop or golf cart.
